Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:11.27,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,710.389)}Kamen Rider Dies Twice!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:48.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The new secret organization that took\NShocker's place, Geldam-Shocker,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:50.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,under the leadership of Japan\NBranch chief, General Black,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,came after the Kamen Rider with\Nthe powerful monster Ganikomoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.22,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was a long, brutal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:03.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But an aerial dogfight between\NKamen Rider and Ganikomoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:07.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ended with both plunging\Ninto the ocean in flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.16,0:02:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider isn't dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He might already be back at the Rider\NCorps HQ, waiting for us to join him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, girls, let's get back for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.15,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd Kamen Rider do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not true that\NKamen Rider is dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.90,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's not true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he is dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, this is no time for crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.05,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know for sure that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We still have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the Kamen Rider is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the Kamen Rider Kid Corps remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The chairman is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, we need to fight the\Nterrible Gel Shocker with our power alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect peace and justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Who sent that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a funeral arrangement...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Our deepest condolences\Nfor the death of the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black, Geldam-Shocker\NJapan Branch Head."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nasty thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.18,0:04:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time bomb! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.45,0:04:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible lengths to\Nwhich Gel Shocker will go...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and that impudent Rider Kid Corps\Nwill be crippled by our present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to take advantage of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see that Gel Shocker\Nis off to an orderly start.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.12,0:05:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But one potential liability remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The failed scientists\Nof the former Shocker, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you rid us of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I plan to release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.49,0:05:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Release them, General Black?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.98,0:05:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Release them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll do it in my own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, scientists.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black has decided,\Nin his great magnanimity,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to release you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Release us? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see my wife and child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.94,0:06:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd resigned myself to execution...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really going to release us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black does not lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In ten minutes,\Nyou will leave here in a bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for departure immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't just release people\Nwho know so many of Shocker's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This might prove useful, just in case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.89,0:07:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years since I\Nlast saw the outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That blue sky and green mountains\Nare a sight for sore eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,Are they really just going to send us home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are we stopping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the bus break down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know my way around a machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can help if there's a breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a breakdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're running an experiment here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,An experiment? What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker is executing a deadly plan to
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill all of the people\Nin the Greater Tokyo area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be the guinea pigs for that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.60,0:07:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! That's not what we were promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black said he was releasing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were told you'd be released.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.72,0:08:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We never promised you\Nwould be released alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! I won't go down that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker cyborg, Scorpiontokagesu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.87,0:08:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My body is filled with a gas that will\Ndestroy all oxygen in the air instantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now perform the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:53.07,Italics,,0,0,0,,General Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:57.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,The oxygen-killing gas that Shocker\Ndeveloped has proved remarkably effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:01.19,Italics,,0,0,0,,If we release fifty kilograms\Nof the gas into the skies above Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.27,Italics,,0,0,0,,we can kill ten million\Npeople in an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to wait for\Nyour report to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Check the bodies of the\Ndeceased human guinea pigs,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.21,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,then dispose of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,One left, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.94,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.01,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't have gotten far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.37,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Try the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die until I see my wife again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I put on a brave front for the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've really lost\Nthe will to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.27,0:10:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My dreams, my hopes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I find enough peace of mind\Nto continue the fight against evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.13,0:10:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.81,0:10:53.74,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs55\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Mine Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This woman's husband, Shintaro Mine,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:05.32,Narrator,,0,0,0,,left for South America a year\Nago to study contagious diseases there,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:06.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but has since gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.18,Italics,,0,0,0,,He sent me a postcard after he arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:12.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,but I haven't heard anything since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:17.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Darling... where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your husband, Shintaro Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:53.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs55\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}Mine Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No one's followed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker must not have noticed my escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No sign of him in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.86,0:12:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So he hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But we know he'll come soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.77,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Set up an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.67,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew he'd come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The stubborn fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run, or your pretty little wife dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that disguise has us fooled?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your mind, Shintaro Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm as sane as can be,\NScorpiontokagesu of Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo! You survived?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wounded in the battle with Ganikomoru,\Nbut Doctor Mine nursed me back to health.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.68,0:13:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest easy. Your husband is safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very fortunate to run into\Nyou here while cleaning up business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When I kill you, the name of Scorpiontokagesu\Nwill live forever in the annals of Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, get to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:14:00.65,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.13,0:14:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.89,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker... I will fight you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hongo! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! You think you can\Nfight me in your condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a little more time to fight\Nthis cyborg on equal footing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've not fully recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.42,0:15:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, I've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.04,0:15:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Double Hold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpiontokagesu...\Nwe'll finish this another day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true? You're sure of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.64,0:15:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshiko, you're sure of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.47,0:15:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So he really is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great! Kamen Rider forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling he'd be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! You were the\Nbiggest wreck of all of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you crying in\Nthe bathroom, too, Yokko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to tell the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this Hongo? Taki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.53,0:16:12.80,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have a message for the Kamen Rider\NKid Corps acting under Captain Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,General Black...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the Kamen Rider this:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker currently holds
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the lives of the 10 million residents\Nof Greater Tokyo in our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're about to remove all the\Noxygen from the skies above Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.01,0:16:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have thirty minutes until this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask Mine there if it's possible or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpiontokagesu's oxygen-killing\Ngas really is that powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your message for Kamen Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one condition:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider must submit\Nto Gel Shocker's scalpel,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we can make him\Na cyborg fully under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This action will save\Nthe lives of 10 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet him at the Kamen\NRider training grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider training grounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's where Chairman Tachibana is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You already killed Takeshi...\NWhat more could you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the Kamen Rider merely\Nlet you think he was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to try to get the drop on Gel Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on his way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that Hongo is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.83,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We nearly fell for your little act,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,which allowed him to almost foil\Nour Operation: Bloodless Tokyo Takeover.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Hongo is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.19,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is now the time to celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana... we're going to\Nuse you to finish off Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Use me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know that Hongo is alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never let you use me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly die for our cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'll rather kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.61,0:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, to help Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you die that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki Kazuya is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... capture him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The fool! Coming here\Nin complete ignorance...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.05,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the plan, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We prevent Scorpiontokagesu from\Nunleashing his oxygen-killing gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.08,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.78,0:20:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Look after Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... I'll unleash the\Noxygen-killing gas right before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.85,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, you'll never\Ninterfere with us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind direction is perfect\Nto carry the oxygen-killing gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.81,0:21:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, 10 million people will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.52,0:21:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Scorpiontokagesu's weak point is his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for his back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Reverse Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider! I'm so glad you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I worried you, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.\NI'm just glad you're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, you should thank\Nthe Mine family, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.17,0:22:55.19,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Geldam-Shocker's monster Scorpiontokagesu\Nwas defeated by the Kamen Rider,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:22:59.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but General Black already has\Na terrifying new plan in the wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:02.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ride on, Kamen Rider, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.17,0:23:10.80,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:14.98,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(280.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:14.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A mysterious shadow creeps up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:21.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I, the deadly Kurage Wolf, will use the\N30,000 volts of electricity at my command
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.67,0:23:24.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to turn Tokyo into an inferno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:31.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider! I can't wait\Nto throw down with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,215.389)}The Monstrous Kurage Wolf
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,715.389)}The Rush Hour of Terror
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:50.54,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:57.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.71,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.71,0:24:05.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.53,0:24:09.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider Dies Twice!!
Comment: 0,0:23:26.53,0:23:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Kurage Wolf\NThe Rush Hour of Terror